plot: Internet 'ce-webrity', Perez Hilton, navigates the red carpet of Las Vegas' Hard Rock Hotel like a modern day Capote. Perez seeks out his next bit of gossip while he looks for a little bit of face time with his namesake herself, Paris Hilton
title: Perez Hilton: Gossip Queen
